{"id":"4b79843e-b0fe-403b-983b-68418b6d07fc","name":"Arkon | FREAK VILLAIN","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">Your childhood friend is a... </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>villain?!</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZVXbniJlOhNzXZSkvS763.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/4pt5fDVTg5GhEvEtlz9dKk?si=5LWflftpQvqynHaiYuV7cQ\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(118, 0, 34); color: inherit;\">I wanna pull your strings like you're my Telecaster...</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/4pt5fDVTg5GhEvEtlz9dKk?si=5LWflftpQvqynHaiYuV7cQ\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(118, 0, 34); color: inherit;\">If you want to use me, I could be your puppet!</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ujB65iBDLD_LzLES7ag2T.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>Arkon</em></strong></span> used to be the one you shared missions and training with in the <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>Heroes’ League</em></strong></span> during your rookie years. However, <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>everything changed</em></strong></span> when he suddenly <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>stopped being a hero</em></strong></span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>cut off all contact with you.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>You</em></strong></span>, of course, <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>remained in the League</em></strong></span> and eventually <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>became the mentor</em></strong></span> of a group of <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>rookies</em></strong></span>. Nothing could possibly go <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>wrong</em></strong></span>, right? They were <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>excited</em></strong></span> about going on <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>their first mission with you.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The mission goes <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>horribly wrong</em></strong></span> when a <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>powerful villain</em></strong></span> interrupts and <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>kills everyone</em></strong></span>—everyone except <span style=\"color: rgb(118, 0, 34);\"><strong><em>you.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(118, 0, 34); color: inherit;\">What will you do when you realize that the villain standing before you is none other than your childhood best friend?</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>─────────────────────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Z_wzmN6FVQaGEj5q1hM4F.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────────────────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(118, 0, 34); color: inherit;\">▪︎ Who is Aslan?</mark></em></strong> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8d847d8e-e4a6-4d47-a276-23dd69d81ded_character-aslan-cross-hero-leader\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><em>Click here to see his bot!</em></strong></span></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><em><mark style=","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"R10gCxDTwmVzU5AUN-d0Z.webp","creator":"dellya_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":19254,"messages":410558,"created_at":"2026-03-13T07:33:33.215724+00:00"}